sources.description:
Rich Kids - A group of troubled teens from a low-income community break into "Los Ricos", the local mansion with a border fence, and spend the day pretending to be rich in order to forget their difficult lives.
2018.  Stars: Gerardo M Velasquez, Justin Rodriguez, Michelle Magallon

metadata.Plot: The movie is about a group of young, beautiful and most of all rich kids, who try to drown their parents neglect in booze, drugs and sex. They all live in the richest neighborhoods in Denmark with designer clothes, yachts and cars. They might look cool from the outside, but in their environment everything is about power, money and respect, and none of them can handle the pressure of constantly proving themselves to the group.
metadata.Actors: Simone Aagaard-Hansen, Lotte Arnsbjerg, Rune Bendixen
